* Solar_Filter::numeric() -- Returns only numbers within the value.

* Solar_Filter::pregReplace() -- Applies a [[php preg_replace()]] filter.

* Solar_Filter::strReplace() -- Applies a [[php str_replace()]] filter.

* Solar_Filter::stripAlnum() -- Strips alphanumeric characters from the value.

* Solar_Filter::stripAlpha() -- Strips alphabetic characters from the value.

* Solar_Filter::stripBlanks() -- Strips all whitespace from the value.

* Solar_Filter::stripNumeric() -- Strips all numbers from the value.

* Solar_Filter::stripWords() -- Strips word characters from the value.

* Solar_Filter::trim() -- Trims characters from the beginning and end of the value.

* Solar_Filter::words() -- Returns only word characters within the value.

